    <br>
    Yuin Starchaser says 'To craft an Art Keepers Robe you will require three 
    [silk thread], giant wasp warrior pollen, two woven spider silks, and a 
    pristine forest drakeling scales. Once you have the necessary components 
    combine them in your Curing Kit with this Tattered Robe Pattern.</p>
